{"type": "article", "id": 62277, "title": "2020 东京奥运火炬揭晓，灵感来自樱花｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-03-21T22:32:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 57412, "name": "Objects of Common Interest"}, {"id": 57413, "name": "Jupiter 10"}, {"id": 1277, "name": "IKEA"}, {"id": 46374, "name": "Tokujin Yoshioka"}, {"id": 24975, "name": "Brain Dead"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 137, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190321215052P7CJEbvKZo8B6wWx.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} </style>  </p><h3>The 2020 Olympic torch by Tokujin Yoshioka </h3><p>日本奥组委正式揭晓 2020 年东京夏季奥运会火炬，全长 71 厘米，重量 1.2 千克，出自日本设计大师吉冈德仁（Tokujin Yoshioka）之手。据称其灵感源自日本国花樱花，整个火炬呈现出粉亮质感的樱花金色，还采用了和日本新干线列车相同的高端制作工艺。</p><p>火炬的顶部被设计成花瓣状，火种将先从 5 个花瓣分别燃起再汇聚到中心形成圣火。值得一提的是，制成火炬的铝制材料是由 2011 日本大地震灾区临时住房的建材回收而来，象征着希望与和平。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215126GmCepckW2qF0HQK6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215127G2HlNan6cEqC8y4X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666947\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215127Aqsnu0gIpDdRTS9O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215128rY9Df2J3kQXPFlt5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.999577\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903212151279FJ4DT1kYbOQmX8I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215131MwPALo07NxFsHJ3c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Home Goods by Brain Dead</h3><p>洛杉矶街头品牌素来以创意搞怪、脑洞大开而闻名。最近，它们推出了一系列趣味十足的家居品 Home Goods 系列。</p><p>整个系列包括以招牌人头 Logo 为造型的蜡烛、线香座、肥皂，卡通小便池造型的恶搞地毯、印有实验风格图案的靠枕，以及狗狗项圈、挂绳和线香等多种选择，可以成为你增添日常生活趣味的不俗之选。售价 25 美元起，<a href=\"https://wearebraindead.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215216wvRqoksPl631dg5X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215216u8MXzT90yoJfjK72.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666990\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215216Czomgl3WE2YhSG7L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215217RbCSxIYNsL8DFnXV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215217oWXvyd7N5S1RUZM6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215217PRwIk7l9DYQEOb8p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019032121521896J3fOR8KgjexqPG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215218DEKMdrwVqzjHlLIc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215218Yf6adrIXMxLAqkzn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215219NuWkHZBPrECyA1cL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wildhomes for Wildlife project by IKEA worked with UK artists and designers</h3><p>宜家为了纪念其在格林威治开设的分店，邀请到了当地的艺术家，一起为野生动物们创造了一系列“住宅”。这些由宜家的桌子、灯具和椅子搭建而成的巢穴适用于从鸟类、蝙蝠到松鼠、蜜蜂等各种动物。</p><p>设计师 Je Ahn 把宜家经典的 Kvistbro 铁质桌子，改造成了一个能够为蝙蝠提供温暖的窝。该活动不仅宣传了宜家的新店，还呼吁人们加强对于环境和野生动物的保护。同时，宜家还借此声明其全球 6 成以上的家具都是用可再生的材料制成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215251Okj7KcwPDuYqCisG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215250EfmxDKUTjsCNteLh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215251g5LbThVSrUtAOljJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903212152523wKCETW0VivSZstD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903212152534fFlvODE0XxJPR9Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215254RhYkluKswy4qGPrj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215254aEbYUDHpCRzNcIVF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://motherlondon.com/work/ikea-wildhomes-for-wildlife/\" rel=\"nofollow\">motherlondon</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Stripe Collection by Jupiter 10</h3><p>英国墙饰品牌 Jupiter 10 是 Bruno Basso 和 Christopher Brooke 合作创立的品牌，大胆地使用色彩和他们著名作品的图形元素，带有一种全新的现代感。第一批推向市场的作品是现代主义墙饰的独家系列，将传统的力量与技术创新结合在一起，是对中世纪现代设计的重新构想。</p><p>最近，Jupiter 10 又推出了 Stripe 系列壁纸，通过创建垂直、水平甚至交织在一起的图案来探索最易识别的元素之一条纹。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215901tCU8vZnRBM9ErSlm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215345C9LvlcWPsXEiBeYI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215348EbVi1TS0hlAspBQF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215354LPDnhyNEMZTkogdK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215407sR4iuGwrgMtlS7zm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215408Hyk1zNrjKFR5pMYv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215414EpWTtaIv2UwMg04K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215414wKX6nrZ5J2Bf7FoT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.jupiter10.com/shop-stripes\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jupiter 10</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Landscape by Objects of Common Interest</h3><p>在今年纽约的 Collective Design 展览上，在线杂志  Sight Unseen 联合雅典设计工作室 Objects of Common Interest 对展位进行总体方案设计，此外，还创造了一个名为 Landscape 的沉浸式装置。</p><p>Landscape 由三个独特的组件组成，共同创造反射镜像静物。第一个元素管灯，是一系列发光的弯曲形状。第二个是 Formations II，一个软垫雕塑座椅的集合。第三个是 Blow Chair，一个柔软的雕塑，也可作为休息区域。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215603N31jRbia0zIA92pY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.433333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215605zhHkYSM8FGgKwl5O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.433333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215616G81yUCKgI2H4aOq0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215631fMdapeslmvO8NErX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215716i2uty8HG0SERNTVo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190321215716XCxReBsThuqfOS5U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/sight-unseen-showcases-objects-of-common-interest-at-collective-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><br></p>"}